sequenceDiagram
    actor Sender as Authenticated user
    participant Frontend as React chat UI
    participant API as Symfony API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Mercure as Mercure Hub
    participant Receiver as Other subscribed client

    Sender->>Frontend: Type message and submit
    Frontend->>API: POST /api/workspaces/{workspaceId}/channels/{channelId}/messages
    API->>DB: Check channel membership
    DB-->>API: Membership confirmed
    API->>DB: Persist message
    DB-->>API: Message saved
    API->>Mercure: Publish message event
    Mercure-->>Receiver: SSE update
    API-->>Frontend: 201 Created + message payload
    Mercure-->>Frontend: Optional live echo or refresh
